1
00:00:01,140 --> 00:00:03,580
(Episode 111)

2
00:00:29,970 --> 00:00:30,970
I'm so scared.

3
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:32,840
Help me.

4
00:00:33,670 --> 00:00:34,670
Jang Mi.

5
00:00:35,610 --> 00:00:36,610
Mom.

6
00:00:40,510 --> 00:00:41,510
Seo Rin.

7
00:00:42,950 --> 00:00:45,720
Thank you for being my daughter
all this time.

8
00:00:47,450 --> 00:00:48,950
Now, you can rest in peace.

9
00:00:50,090 --> 00:00:51,390
What...

10
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:52,690
What does that mean?

11
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:55,260
Are you trying to kill me, Mom?

12
00:00:55,890 --> 00:00:57,000
This can't be happening.

13
00:00:57,860 --> 00:00:58,860
Chae Hwa Young!

14
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:11,980
After some sleep, everything will be done.

15
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,750
Sleep well, Seo Rin.

16
00:02:20,410 --> 00:02:21,580
Goodbye, my daughter.

17
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:25,020
Mom. Chae Hwa Young.

18
00:02:25,620 --> 00:02:27,220
You're not going to do something to me,
are you?

19
00:02:27,650 --> 00:02:30,260
Right? Tell me you're not.

20
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:32,190
Say it.

21
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:44,740
No! Don't kill me.

22
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:48,210
Chae Hwa Young, please, let me live.
I don't want to die!

23
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:50,210
Chae Hwa Young.

24
00:02:50,580 --> 00:02:51,840
How could you...

25
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,880
Jang Mi.

26
00:02:54,450 --> 00:02:55,580
Mom.

27
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:57,820
Save me.

28
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,120
Mom...

29
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:01,920
Jang Mi...

30
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:08,530
Mom,

31
00:03:09,260 --> 00:03:14,230
I was so happy when we went
on that picnic with Jang Mi.

32
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,070
I'm sorry,

33
00:03:17,970 --> 00:03:18,970
Jang Mi.

34
00:03:20,170 --> 00:03:21,170
Mom.

35
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:24,010
Goodbye.

36
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,700
Jang Mi! Are you okay?

37
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,830
I can't breathe...

38
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:48,130
I can't breathe...

39
00:03:48,730 --> 00:03:49,830
That ringing...

40
00:03:53,370 --> 00:03:55,370
I can't breathe...

41
00:03:55,370 --> 00:03:56,770
I can't breathe.

42
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:59,980
Jang Mi, try to take a deep breath. Okay?

43
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:11,460
Something feels really wrong.

44
00:04:12,790 --> 00:04:13,860
I think...

45
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:15,890
Goodness. Jang Mi!

46
00:04:15,890 --> 00:04:19,230
Jang Mi!

47
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:29,170
Mom! What's wrong? Mom!

48
00:04:30,170 --> 00:04:31,180
Mom!

49
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:32,710
Mom!

50
00:04:48,530 --> 00:04:49,530
It's over.

51
00:04:50,260 --> 00:04:53,060
The thorn in my side is finally gone.

52
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,830
Why did you have to find out secrets
you weren't meant to know...

53
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:58,870
and rush to your own death?

54
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:04,810
No, Seo Rin!

55
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,180
Seo Rin... No!

56
00:05:08,450 --> 00:05:12,280
Oh, please, Ma Seo Rin!

57
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:17,290
Doctor, please save my Seo Rin!

58
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:21,130
Don't leave your mom, Seo Rin.

59
00:05:21,690 --> 00:05:24,260
Seo Rin, open your eyes. Seo Rin.

60
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:27,230
Don't leave me behind.

61
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:32,170
- My dear Seo Rin.
- Are you okay? Mom!

62
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,440
Mom!

63
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:36,840
Seo Rin!

64
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:39,580
Doctor, please...

65
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,390
How's your mom?

66
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,090
She's sick in Tae Sook's room.

67
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:58,260
What's wrong with both of them
all of a sudden?

68
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:01,630
You don't think it's something contagious,
do you?

69
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:03,030
I know, right?

70
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:05,070
Should we take them to the hospital?

71
00:06:07,570 --> 00:06:08,710
Seo Rin!

72
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:09,740
Seo Rin?

73
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:11,710
Seo Rin!

74
00:06:19,450 --> 00:06:20,520
Seo Rin!

75
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,790
Seo Rin!

76
00:06:29,290 --> 00:06:30,290
Seo Rin!

77
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:35,300
Seo Rin. Why are your hands so cold?
Are you sick?

78
00:06:36,670 --> 00:06:39,370
What's wrong? Did something happen?

79
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:47,510
I'm sorry.

80
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,990
No!

81
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:04,900
Don't take Seo Rin away!
Seo Rin! Ma Seo Rin!

82
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:07,430
Seo Rin, don't go! Ma Seo Rin!

83
00:07:07,770 --> 00:07:08,970
Seo Rin!

84
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,140
Ma Seo Rin!

85
00:07:13,170 --> 00:07:15,240
- Seo Rin.
- Jang Mi.

86
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:17,540
- Seo Rin.
- Jang Mi.

87
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:18,610
Seo Rin!

88
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,950
Baek Ho.

89
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:24,250
Jang Mi, are you okay?

90
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:26,780
- Are you sure you don't need a doctor?
- Seo Rin...

91
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:29,150
- What?
- Seo Rin...

92
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:31,620
I'm certain something happened to Seo Rin.

93
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:33,890
I have to go to Seo Rin.

94
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:36,390
- Wait, Jang Mi.
- Seo Rin!

95
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:41,500
Father!

96
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,670
What is it now?

97
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:47,040
It's Seo Rin...

98
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,940
What am I going to do? Seo Rin...

99
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:52,040
What about Seo Rin?

100
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:56,310
- He'll call you back later.
- Just spit it out!

101
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:58,120
What about Seo Rin?

102
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:02,350
Seo Rin was getting plastic surgery...

103
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:06,360
What? Go on and tell me!

104
00:08:06,690 --> 00:08:10,860
What happened to Seo Rin
during her plastic surgery?

105
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:12,960
She went into cardiac arrest.

106
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,830
Seo Rin's dead, Father!

107
00:08:16,730 --> 00:08:17,870
My poor Seo Rin...

108
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:21,940
- died on the operating table, Father.
- Goodness!

109
00:08:22,010 --> 00:08:23,010
Sir!

110
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:24,510
Pull yourself together, sir.

111
00:08:27,410 --> 00:08:30,450
Honey!

112
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:34,050
- Call Doctor Kim. Now!
- Yes, right away.

113
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:40,890
Doctor Kim, the Chairman has collapsed.

114
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,830
Please, get here as fast as you can.

115
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,130
What do we do?

116
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:48,230
- Seo Rin...
- What happened to Seo Rin?

117
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,330
She's dead.

118
00:08:51,170 --> 00:08:53,400
She died during plastic surgery.

119
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:55,110
Jang Mi.

120
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:58,680
No... That's a lie, right?

121
00:08:59,310 --> 00:09:01,910
This can't be happening.
No, this can't be right.

122
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,310
No...

123
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,480
No, it can't be, Seo Rin!

124
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:14,530
Seo Rin, how could you leave like this?
What am I supposed to do now?

125
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,360
Oh, dear.

126
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:20,030
Goodness. Try to calm down.

127
00:09:20,330 --> 00:09:22,730
Tell me exactly what happened.

128
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:27,570
Seo Rin said she wanted
to get plastic surgery on her face,

129
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,140
and I guess she found a clinic on her own.

130
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:32,940
She went to get the surgery by herself...

131
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,650
and suddenly went into cardiac arrest.

132
00:09:35,650 --> 00:09:37,450
So they called me.

133
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,080
I guess she put me down as her guardian.

134
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:43,750
But why would a perfectly healthy girl
just go into cardiac arrest?

135
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:46,820
According to the doctor,
before the surgery,

136
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:49,230
Seo Rin had probably taken
a prohibited diet...

137
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:50,830
or sleeping pills
she wasn't supposed to take.

138
00:09:51,300 --> 00:09:54,270
They told her to declare it
on the pre-op questionnaire,

139
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,840
but I guess she didn't.

140
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:02,010
Seo Rin was taking diet pills, you know.

141
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,670
She took sleeping pills sometimes, too.

142
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:08,580
Why wouldn't she mention that
and let this happen?

143
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:10,820
Goodness, what are we going to do?

144
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,550
My poor Seo Rin...

145
00:10:15,590 --> 00:10:17,090
It should have been me.

146
00:10:17,890 --> 00:10:19,160
My beautiful girl...

147
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,830
This way...

148
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:28,730
I'm sorry, Seo Rin...

149
00:10:30,170 --> 00:10:33,740
Seo Rin, how could you leave your mom...

150
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,380
Tell me the truth, Chae Hwa Young.

151
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:44,550
You killed Seo Rin, didn't you?

152
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,450
What did you do to my Seo Rin?

153
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:53,060
Why did my Seo Rin have to die?
Tell me why my Seo Rin is dead!

154
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:59,230
My daughter, Seo Rin...

155
00:11:00,130 --> 00:11:01,670
My daughter, Seo Rin, is dead.

156
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:05,040
- I'm the one who killed her.
- Stop the act!

157
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:09,870
You're the one who killed Seo Rin. Right?

158
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,880
Bring Seo Rin back, you murderer!

159
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:15,450
Jang Mi, calm down. Please, calm down.

160
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:20,380
Let go of me!
She's the one who killed my Seo Rin!

161
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,320
Chae Hwa Young!

162
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,160
What am I going to do, Seo Rin?

163
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:30,260
No, Seo Rin.

164
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:41,710
Jun Ho,
about Chairman Ma's biological daughter...

165
00:11:42,070 --> 00:11:43,940
Has CEO Chae found out anything new?

166
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:47,210
If you know something, fill me in.

167
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:48,410
And what would you do if you knew?

168
00:11:49,850 --> 00:11:51,450
Are you going to go and stop her yourself?

169
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:55,450
Why would I stop her?

170
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:57,390
CEO Chae will handle it.

171
00:11:57,590 --> 00:12:01,960
I just need to know what's happening
so I can be prepared.

172
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:04,260
I thought you said
we were in the same boat.

173
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:06,600
You said this was supposed to be
a win-win for us.

174
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,910
- Mom? What's up?
- Hong Ju.

175
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:18,110
Hong Ju, this is awful.

176
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:21,010
They're saying Seo Rin is dead.

177
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:23,980
What? Who's dead?

178
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,980
Seo Rin?

179
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:28,350
She went to get plastic surgery,

180
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:30,520
but apparently she was abusing drugs,

181
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:33,590
which caused cardiac arrest.

182
00:12:33,660 --> 00:12:35,560
My goodness. That's impossible.

183
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:37,700
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

184
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,100
Is that really true?

185
00:12:41,130 --> 00:12:42,930
Seo Rin died during surgery?

186
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:45,740
That's what they're saying.
The chairman collapsed,

187
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:48,340
and everyone's a complete mess.

188
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:52,510
We have to plan a funeral...
I can't believe this is happening.

189
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:53,810
How could this have happened...

190
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:57,680
(Ohjeong Plastic Surgery)

191
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:59,650
(Caution)

192
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:04,420
I sent the death certificate
under the name Oh Jang Mi.

193
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,660
Yes.

194
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:09,990
Right.

195
00:13:12,330 --> 00:13:15,330
(Hospital Director Kim Gyu Jin,
Ohjeong Plastic Surgery)

196
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:23,210
(Ohjeong Plastic Surgery CCTV)

197
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:25,980
(This folder is empty.)

198
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:31,950
Who's there? We're closed.

199
00:13:33,220 --> 00:13:34,220
You're...

200
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:37,490
(Hospital Director Kim Gyu Jin,
Ohjeong Plastic Surgery)

201
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:40,160
Why does it look like you've seen a ghost?

202
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,490
Do you think Seo Rin, the girl you killed,
came back from the grave?

203
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:43,930
Who are you?

204
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:45,900
Why did Seo Rin die of cardiac arrest?

205
00:13:46,230 --> 00:13:48,670
- She was perfectly healthy. Why?
- Let me go.

206
00:13:49,230 --> 00:13:52,170
I don't know.
She took a prohibited drug beforehand.

207
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:55,240
I already told the police everything.
I did nothing wrong!

208
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,340
You expect us to believe that?

209
00:14:00,950 --> 00:14:04,010
If you're so innocent, why are you
shredding your ledger at night?

210
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:06,580
Tell me the truth.
Did Chae Hwa Young put you up to this?

211
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:08,450
What do you think you're doing?

212
00:14:09,350 --> 00:14:12,160
Do an autopsy or whatever. I don't care.

213
00:14:12,190 --> 00:14:16,060
How was I supposed to know
she took a prohibited drug beforehand?

214
00:14:16,490 --> 00:14:19,330
The person who took a drug like that
is the one at fault.

215
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,470
I'm innocent.

216
00:14:33,940 --> 00:14:34,950
You wanted to see me?

217
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:36,550
Team Leader Jin.

218
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:42,720
I want you to be in charge of the funeral,
starting with setting up the memorial.

219
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,560
What? Why me?

220
00:14:45,620 --> 00:14:47,730
You're probably the only one
at the Chairman's house...

221
00:14:47,730 --> 00:14:48,890
who can think straight right now.

222
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:50,130
Even so...

223
00:14:50,690 --> 00:14:52,700
Why should I handle Seo Rin's funeral?

224
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:54,030
Didn't you say we were in the same boat?

225
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:56,070
That it would be a win-win for both of us?

226
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:05,280
(Room One: Oh Jang Mi)

227
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:07,210
(Mother: Jung Suk Hee,
Siblings: Oh Tae Sook, Oh Tae Pyung)

228
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:13,450
(Oh Jang Mi)

229
00:15:17,590 --> 00:15:20,190
What? What did Jun Ho do?

230
00:15:20,660 --> 00:15:23,390
The patient who died during the operation
wasn't Ma Seo Rin.

231
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:25,500
It was Oh Jang Mi.

232
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:31,070
I see.

233
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:34,040
That's my son, all right.

234
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:37,370
He's even more ruthless
and meticulous than I am.

235
00:15:37,710 --> 00:15:40,140
I had the doctor issue a death certificate
under Oh Jang Mi's name...

236
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:41,410
and gave it to Jun Ho.

237
00:15:41,950 --> 00:15:45,180
The problem is that you need to convince
Chairman Ma right now...

238
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:47,690
to file the death certificate
and proceed with the funeral...

239
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:50,090
under Oh Jang Mi's name.

240
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:52,460
You're right. I have to go.

241
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:55,890
My son has set the stage so perfectly.

242
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:58,330
It's up to me as his mother
to go and tie up the loose ends.

243
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:02,630
Now, Oh Jang Mi will cease to exist,

244
00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:05,370
and only Ma Seo Rin, your daughter,

245
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:08,240
will be the only one to exist.

246
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,080
I never needed both of them
from the start.

247
00:16:11,810 --> 00:16:13,940
One is all I ever needed.

248
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:21,390
Father.

249
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:23,450
We can't let the world know...

250
00:16:24,860 --> 00:16:26,620
about Seo Rin's death.

251
00:16:27,730 --> 00:16:29,630
What are you talking about?

252
00:16:30,330 --> 00:16:31,700
You viper.

253
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:36,470
You're the one who pushed my granddaughter
onto that operating table,

254
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:37,940
and now you're saying this?

255
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:41,070
"We can't let the world know?"

256
00:16:41,570 --> 00:16:43,710
As for my Seo Rin's death,

257
00:16:43,970 --> 00:16:46,010
if I find out...

258
00:16:46,510 --> 00:16:48,380
you were involved,

259
00:16:48,980 --> 00:16:52,580
I'll throw you in jail myself.
So you just wait.

260
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:57,150
How could you think I'd do something
to the daughter I raised for 30 years?

261
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:01,560
This isn't fair. I didn't even know
Seo Rin was going to the hospital.

262
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:02,730
Shut up!

263
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:05,660
Do you think I don't know
what you're like?

264
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:10,430
Start preparing Seo Rin's funeral now.

265
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,170
My poor Seo Rin died so tragically.

266
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:17,810
I'm going to give her a send-off
the whole world will hear about.

267
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,810
Now, get out!

268
00:17:20,810 --> 00:17:22,450
What would happen to the company...

269
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:26,150
if an article came out
saying the heir to Dream Hotel died...

270
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:28,720
from narcotic drug use
and medication abuse...

271
00:17:29,390 --> 00:17:30,690
during plastic surgery?

272
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:33,620
The stock price will plummet,
and on top of that,

273
00:17:33,990 --> 00:17:37,030
the entire group could be subject
to a search and seizure.

274
00:17:37,330 --> 00:17:40,230
My own flesh and blood
died a wrongful death.

275
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:42,630
Do you think I care about our stock price?

276
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,270
It's not just about the stock price.

277
00:17:47,910 --> 00:17:49,740
Right now, at the Dream Project office,

278
00:17:49,970 --> 00:17:53,640
Oh Jang Mi, Seo Rin's exact lookalike,
is at work.

279
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:56,550
Father, you have to think about that.

280
00:17:57,480 --> 00:18:00,580
If we hold a big funeral announcing
that Director Ma Seo Rin is dead,

281
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:03,850
but the next morning, her exact look-alike
is parading around the company,

282
00:18:04,590 --> 00:18:08,160
how do you think people are going to react
to a bizarre situation like that?

283
00:18:08,930 --> 00:18:10,990
Eventually, it'll come out
that they were twins,

284
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:13,600
and all our hidden secrets will be dug up.

285
00:18:14,530 --> 00:18:17,530
Not only will your reputation
be ruined, Father,

286
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:19,540
but you'll be a laughingstock
in the press.

287
00:18:19,740 --> 00:18:20,900
You...

288
00:18:21,410 --> 00:18:23,110
You disgusting monster!

289
00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:25,280
Back then...

290
00:18:26,080 --> 00:18:28,810
Back then, I should have turned you in...

291
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:33,780
and told the world the truth back then.

292
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:37,450
Because of my foolish hesitation,

293
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:39,260
I...

294
00:18:41,390 --> 00:18:43,030
You need to make the right decision.

295
00:18:43,690 --> 00:18:45,300
Please, think of the company.

296
00:18:45,430 --> 00:18:46,560
Then...

297
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:50,670
Then what am I supposed to do?

298
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:52,500
The death certificate and funeral...

299
00:18:53,100 --> 00:18:54,940
must be under Oh Jang Mi's name.

300
00:18:55,810 --> 00:18:57,510
Oh Jang Mi is the one who's dead.

301
00:18:58,810 --> 00:19:00,010
We'll have her...

302
00:19:00,540 --> 00:19:02,550
live as Seo Rin.

303
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:07,890
This is how you save your granddaughter,
Seo Rin,

304
00:19:08,490 --> 00:19:10,550
and the only way to save
Dream Hotel's reputation.

305
00:19:21,330 --> 00:19:22,730
Seo Rin...

306
00:19:30,370 --> 00:19:33,740
I gathered every last piece of the ledger.

307
00:19:34,010 --> 00:19:36,550
I'm going to piece it all together,
submit it to the police as evidence,

308
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,350
and request an immediate autopsy.

309
00:19:38,650 --> 00:19:40,450
In the meantime,
you should head to the funeral home.

310
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:41,950
And don't push yourself too hard.

311
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:46,090
A funeral home? Who died?

312
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:52,900
Ma Seo Rin.

313
00:19:55,130 --> 00:19:56,130
What?

314
00:19:56,530 --> 00:19:58,240
Director Ma is dead?

315
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,200
Who's dead?

316
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,670
What do you mean Director Ma is dead?

317
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:04,780
What's in here...

318
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,440
is proof that Chae Hwa Young
bribed a plastic surgeon...

319
00:20:07,840 --> 00:20:09,750
to have Seo Rin killed.

320
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:11,250
Hwa Young killed her own daughter?

321
00:20:11,850 --> 00:20:14,150
Kang Baek Ho, don't be ridiculous.

322
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,420
She wouldn’t have killed
her own daughter...

323
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:18,490
How can you make such
an unthinkable accusation?

324
00:20:18,690 --> 00:20:20,390
I wish it weren't true either.

325
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:23,290
I'm taking this to the police station...

326
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:26,860
to report her for soliciting murder
and request an autopsy.

327
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,970
What...

328
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:31,570
I can't believe this is happening.

329
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:34,100
That beautiful young woman is dead?

330
00:20:35,010 --> 00:20:36,010
My goodness!

331
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:40,780
Seo Rin.

332
00:20:41,450 --> 00:20:42,580
Seo Rin.

333
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:48,590
What is this?

334
00:20:48,590 --> 00:20:49,690
(Oh Jang Mi)

335
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:50,890
Why is my name...

336
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:52,220
(Oh Jang Mi)

337
00:20:52,290 --> 00:20:53,420
Why is my name showing?

338
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:01,500
You're here.

339
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:03,700
Ma Seo Rin.

340
00:21:06,470 --> 00:21:08,870
I don't know what I can say
to comfort you.

341
00:21:12,540 --> 00:21:14,240
May Jang Mi rest in peace.

342
00:21:18,450 --> 00:21:19,450
What?

343
00:21:19,850 --> 00:21:21,690
So they're pretending
Oh Jang Mi is the one who died?

344
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,720
It's what Oh Jang Mi wanted, too.

345
00:21:25,590 --> 00:21:29,390
Wasn't this inevitable from the moment
she entered our house to be Ma Seo Rin?

346
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:33,530
Still, how can you just declare
a living person dead?

347
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,400
Does that even make sense?

348
00:21:35,470 --> 00:21:38,770
CEO Chae has probably convinced
the Chairman by now.

349
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:42,010
My goodness.

350
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:44,540
Find that bastard doctor
who killed Seo Rin...

351
00:21:45,810 --> 00:21:48,580
and bring him to me on his knees.

352
00:21:48,910 --> 00:21:50,850
- Immediately!
- Yes, Chairman.

353
00:21:55,450 --> 00:21:57,690
Grandfather!

354
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:00,390
Grandfather.

355
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:05,060
My name is on the portrait,
not Seo Rin's, at the funeral home.

356
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:06,130
Jang Mi,

357
00:22:07,600 --> 00:22:08,870
I'm so sorry.

358
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:12,700
You knew about this?

359
00:22:14,270 --> 00:22:17,010
Don't tell me you ordered this.

360
00:22:17,770 --> 00:22:21,040
You mean you allowed this to happen?

361
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:23,810
Yes, that's right, reporter.

362
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:28,590
Focus on the surgery's side effects
and the risks of anesthesia.

363
00:22:30,390 --> 00:22:33,190
I'll email you the information
on the deceased, Oh Jang Mi.

364
00:22:33,490 --> 00:22:34,860
So I trust you'll handle the article well.

365
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:42,330
Since Oh Jang Mi is Baek Ho's girlfriend,

366
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,270
it's only right that she be the one
who's dead.

367
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:48,640
I'm the one who's going
to marry Ma Seo Rin, after all.

368
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:55,810
Kang Jun Ho, it was your doing, wasn't it?

369
00:22:56,050 --> 00:22:58,520
You're the one
who made Jang Mi the deceased, didn't you?

370
00:22:58,580 --> 00:23:00,280
That's what Jang Mi wanted.

371
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:04,550
The woman who's alive now isn't Jang Mi.
It's Ma Seo Rin.

372
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,760
What?

373
00:23:08,930 --> 00:23:09,930
Think about it.

374
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:14,300
The one who woke up in the hospital
after that car accident was Ma Seo Rin.

375
00:23:14,430 --> 00:23:16,800
The one who remained hospitalized
was Oh Jang Mi.

376
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:18,740
And the woman...

377
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,970
I was supposed to marry was Ma Seo Rin.

378
00:23:22,710 --> 00:23:23,770
Have you forgotten?

379
00:23:24,170 --> 00:23:26,240
Kang Jun Ho, are you insane?

380
00:23:28,650 --> 00:23:29,810
Listen up.

381
00:23:31,350 --> 00:23:35,420
As of today, the Oh Jang Mi
you were married to is dead.

382
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:39,490
So stay away from my Ma Seo Rin.

383
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:41,490
I'm warning you.

384
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:44,190
If you so much as go near my woman,

385
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:47,130
there's no telling how far I'll go.

386
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,370
No, I'm warning you.

387
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:54,300
I won't let you or Chae Hwa Young
get away with this.

388
00:23:54,840 --> 00:23:56,810
I will risk my own life...

389
00:23:57,740 --> 00:24:00,340
to make you pay for what you've done.
Just you wait.

390
00:24:10,790 --> 00:24:11,960
Seo Rin.

391
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:14,190
Seo Rin.

392
00:24:24,370 --> 00:24:25,440
How is your mother?

393
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:33,480
Tae Pyung could barely talk about
what happened to Seo Rin,

394
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:35,750
but she just kept crying...

395
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,810
until she passed out.

396
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:46,760
Mom!

397
00:24:48,630 --> 00:24:51,800
Tae Pyung, why did you bring Mom here?

398
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,560
She was completely hysterical.

399
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:57,500
She kept shouting
she had to see Seo Rin, broke free,

400
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,870
and fell running in the street.

401
00:24:59,870 --> 00:25:02,870
She had to see her eventually anyway.

402
00:25:04,010 --> 00:25:05,010
He's right.

403
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:08,910
Your mother needs time
to say goodbye to Seo Rin, too.

404
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:15,350
My sweet Tok Hee...

405
00:25:19,190 --> 00:25:20,720
This is all my fault.

406
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:22,690
Because of me,

407
00:25:22,830 --> 00:25:25,700
my sweet Tok Hee is dead.

408
00:25:28,130 --> 00:25:29,130
Mom.

409
00:25:30,470 --> 00:25:32,700
You need to pull yourself together first,
okay?

410
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:35,810
Tok Hee.

411
00:25:35,810 --> 00:25:37,270
My sweet Tok Hee.

412
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:40,980
I'm so sorry.

413
00:25:41,540 --> 00:25:44,680
I feel like I'm being torn to pieces.

414
00:25:51,390 --> 00:25:52,460
- Mom!
- Ma'am!

415
00:25:52,620 --> 00:25:53,690
- Mom!
- Mom!

416
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:57,060
- Ma'am, hold on!
- Mom, wait! Try to get up!

417
00:25:59,500 --> 00:26:01,200
Why is she causing a scene
all the way out here?

418
00:26:08,670 --> 00:26:09,940
You witch!

419
00:26:10,010 --> 00:26:11,210
You evil monster!

420
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:14,310
- Ma'am.
- Mom.

421
00:26:16,380 --> 00:26:17,380
You...

422
00:26:18,210 --> 00:26:22,120
You killed my daughter. You killed her!

423
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:25,560
Bring my daughter back, you monster!

424
00:26:25,890 --> 00:26:30,260
I said bring back my daughter,
my poor Tok Hee!

425
00:26:30,330 --> 00:26:32,330
Let go of me!

426
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:37,070
Get her out of here
before I call the police.

427
00:26:37,370 --> 00:26:39,600
- What are you doing, Ma Seo Rin?
- Ma Seo Rin?

428
00:26:40,570 --> 00:26:42,310
Why should I listen to you?

429
00:26:42,570 --> 00:26:44,940
Right, because you're not a real mother,

430
00:26:45,180 --> 00:26:47,980
you'd never know the heart of a mother
who's lost her child.

431
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:50,210
- What did you just say?
- Chae Hwa Young!

432
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:54,750
I swear I will rip you to shreds.

433
00:26:55,250 --> 00:26:58,220
I'll rip your organs out one by one...

434
00:26:58,460 --> 00:27:02,760
and make you die in agony, Chae Hwa Young!

435
00:27:37,890 --> 00:27:39,530
(The First Man)

436
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:42,000
Do you really think
Jung Suk Hee has regained her sanity?

437
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,070
Do you think she'd recover that easily?

438
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:47,140
- Chae Hwa Young did this, right?
- Mom.

439
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:49,340
Don't you dare lay a finger on Jang Mi.

440
00:27:49,970 --> 00:27:53,140
If you do the same thing to her
that you did to Seo Rin,

441
00:27:53,340 --> 00:27:55,350
I will instantly become your enemy.

442
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:58,580
Brace yourself.
You'll see what becomes of your son.

443
00:27:58,850 --> 00:28:01,950
You're about to find out
what it feels like to lose a child.

444
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:05,160
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
